name: Exploring 3D Virtual Worlds
description: This image, "Exploring 3D Virtual Worlds" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in this process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewer. The inspiration behind this image was my experiences of living, working, traveling and exploring in various 3D immersive virtual worlds within the vast Metaverse.
